    <p class="subhero-subtitle">A one-day, in-person look at what a globally coordinated robot benchmark looks like in practice: talks from the researchers building it, a visit to the EBiM Evaluation Center, and lab tours at the University of Hamburg. You&rsquo;ll see the Mobile FR3 Duo platform the benchmark actually runs on.</p>

